 have done shammy epic twice in the last three weeks. I was the only mage und used Epic pet for the fight. Compared to my fights with the 49 fire pets before the resist changes, Epic pet killed much faster. <br>
Get your fire resist as high as possible (our lvl 54 resist spell stacks with druid buffs, if you cast it first). With fire resist above 200 pet got hit by Rak´s AE a few times, with resists above 300 (bard song) pet resisted most of the spells. <br>
